# Website (Angular)

- Angular app root: `apps/dert-web/src/client/`
- Strict template type checking
- Use existing component library and styles in this app
- Prefer existing services for state before adding new patterns

## Commands
```bash
npm run web:build
npm run web:lint
npm run web:test
```
